Package: avrevol
Type: Package
Title: Average Evolvability Measures
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2023-03-02
Authors@R: c(person("Junya", "Watanabe", email = "jw2098@cam.ac.uk",
            role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9810-5286")))
Description: This small package provides wrapper functions to evaluate
    average evolvability measures in evolutionary quantitative genetics,
    based on the implementation of recursion-based evaluation of moments of
    ratios of quadratic forms in the package qfratio.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/watanabe-j/avrevol
